l-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/detained-protesters-calling-for-hostage-deal-say-they-were-asked-if-theyre-being-paid/00000191-d1cb-d25e-a1f7-d7cb85260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列海岸发现极度濒危吉他鱼的天然苗圃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/nursery-for-critically-endangered-guitarfish-identified-off-israeli-coast/00000191-d12e-dd1c-a19b-d13f67a60000</link><description>小黑鳅吉它鱼栖息在马甘迈克尔的砂岩海湾中，直到达到足以勇敢面对公海的临界尺寸</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:34:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/nursery-for-critically-endangered-guitarfish-identified-off-israeli-coast/00000191-d12e-dd1c-a19b-d13f67a60000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争成为威尼斯电影节的焦点，获奖者声援巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-takes-spotlight-at-venice-film-festival-as-winners-voice-support-for-palestinians/00000191-d11e-df60-a79b-d17fbffd0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦和美国犹太导演都因其电影获奖，直接解决了这一冲突。斯坎达尔·科普蒂说：“我们的电影着眼于道德叙事如何将我们团结在一起......但同时也让我们对他人的痛苦视而不见。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:13:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-takes-spotlight-at-venice-film-festival-as-winners-voice-support-for-palestinians/00000191-d11e-df60-a79b-d17fbffd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院命令司法部长任命新最高法院院长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-orders-justice-minister-to-appoint-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d17e-df60-a79b-d17fd8ed0000</link><description>这项裁决是对以色列质量政府运动提交的请愿书的回应，该请愿书声称司法部长亚里夫·莱文未能推进任命程序并非善意且涉及别有用心</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 12:15:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-orders-justice-minister-to-appoint-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d17e-df60-a79b-d17fd8ed0000</guid></item><item>