ion><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/u-s-finalizing-new-israel-hamas-cease-fire-proposal-despite-skepticism/00000191-ce14-dd1c-a19b-cf35a77b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府的世界末日愿景：将加沙变成约旦河西岸，将约旦河西岸变成加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-task-the-gazafication-of-the-west-bank/00000191-ce12-d214-a393-cfba5b7c0000</link><description>忘掉在本格维尔的诽谤吧：以色列正面临真正陷入泥潭的风险，因为它着眼于对加沙的军事统治，而约旦河西岸的局势正在各个层面升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-task-the-gazafication-of-the-west-bank/00000191-ce12-d214-a393-cfba5b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>来自约旦的恐怖分子在过境点开枪，三名以色列人丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-live/reports-three-rescuers-killed-in-israeli-attack-in-lebanon-drone-sirens-in-north-israel/00000191-cf4f-d25e-a1f7-cfcff8cb0000</link><description>以色列国防军：夜间从黎巴嫩向以色列发射了约 50 枚火箭弹；无人员伤亡 ■ 约旦表示正在调查与以色列边境发生的致命枪击事件，关闭过境点直至另行通知 ■ 加沙消息来源报道，加沙北部救援部门副指挥官在贾巴利亚家中遇袭身亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 01:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-live/reports-three-rescuers-killed-in-israeli-attack-in-lebanon-drone-sirens-in-north-israel/00000191-cf4f-d25e-a1f7-cfcff8cb0000</guid></item><item><title>法院命令释放涉嫌向本格维尔扔沙子的女子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-released-by-court-order/00000191-ce49-d25e-a1f7-cfcb46e60000</link><description>特拉维夫地方法院法官在观看该事件的短视频后中断听证会，随后将嫌疑人软禁，因为整个法庭都在抗议对她的拘留</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:50:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-released-by-court-order/00000191-ce49-d25e-a1f7