ostage-deal/00000191-cd22-deaf-a1f1-cdb7ed5e0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》摄影师拍摄的以色列一周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures-by-haaretz-photographers/00000191-cccc-deaf-a1f1-cdff7af80000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 15:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures-by-haaretz-photographers/00000191-cccc-deaf-a1f1-cdff7af80000</guid></item><item><title>涉嫌向本格维尔扔沙子的女子被关押过夜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-held-in-jail-overnight/00000191-cbc4-d359-a5f9-dfed93970000</link><description>地方法院接受了警方的说法，即如果嫌疑人被释放，调查可能会受到影响。嫌疑人的母亲在X上写道：“独裁警察决定危及我患有慢性疾病的女儿的生命”</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 09:47:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-held-in-jail-overnight/00000191-cbc4-d359-a5f9-dfed93970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列狱警拍摄虐待被拘留者的视频；监狱部门称这是一次“例行演习”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-guards-filmed-abusing-detainees-prison-service-says-its-a-routine-exercise/00000191-cb71-d359-a5f9-dffd26f60000</link><description>《国土报》获得的照片和视频显示，数十名被拘留者戴着手铐趴在地上，其中一些人赤身裸体，一只看门狗在他们上方狂吠。监狱内并没有发生什么异常事件促使狱警采取行动</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 08:24:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-guards-filmed-abusing-detainees-prison-service-says-its-a-routine-exercise/00000191-cb71-d359-a5f9-dffd26f60000</guid></item><item><title>报道：三名救援人员在以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击中丧生；以色列北部的无人机警报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-live/palestinians-idf-gunfire-kills-13-year-old-girl-in-west-bank-following-settler-clashes/00000191-c8fb-d74e-aff9-ccffedac0